{"tid":736254,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"劏房、高地價和高樓價代價，就係最終變高近視及高散光社會","createTime":"2018-07-10T06:07:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T06:45:31.000Z","uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f3a57536bf2d1d458c7e3bd5852ca2e6b75a307a","tid":736254,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T06:07:12.000Z","msg":"香港屋太細，空間太少<br />\n最好省地方的方法係點<br />\n除左租迷你倉和向高發展的傢俬外<br />\n<br />\n就係<br />\n1 拋棄實體書本、紙張雜誌。全面電子化，數碼化<br />\n2 電視、電腦太阻地方。轉用notebook。<br />\n3 Notebook其實都晒位，轉晒用tablet好過。<br />\n4 tablet都晒位，全部用晒smartphone和cloud services搞掂。<br />\n<br />\n結果就係日日夜夜對住部智能手機<br />\n<br />\n而智能手機，比電視和電腦更易傷眼。<br />\n<br />\n相信未來香港班10後，平均千度近視不是夢。"},{"pid":"f19934bd0ec1b90245e9580cb04fac81f5ec9178","tid":736254,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T06:24:34.000Z","msg":"Phone狂新世紀1歲B已玩手機<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170804/mobile/odn-20170804-0804_00176_081.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170804%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20170804-0804_00176_081.html&d=G3HZ6pmG21M7rxM7%2BVX0Bf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=f06ada51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170804/mobile/odn-20170804-0804_00176_081.html</a><br />\n<br />\n衛署調查：港童1歲已玩手機<br />\n學者﹕沒家長陪同控制 過度活躍風險增<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170804/s00002/1501782962880\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170804%2Fs00002%2F1501782962880&d=G3HZ6pmG21M7rxM7%2BVX0Bf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=69fc4cc1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170804%2Fs00002%2F1501782962880&h=83458b58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170804/s00002/1501782962880</a><br />\n<br />\n理大眼科視光學院研究發現本港學童近視加深趨勢<b